text: Unknown Hinson (born November 7, 1954) is a singer and voice actor. He is known as the voice of Early Cuyler on the adult swim program Squidbillies, from 2005 to 2019, after which he was replaced by Tracy Morgan for itsb 13th and final season in 2021. His real name is Stuart Daniel Baker. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1954 births Category:Adult Swim
